{"tid":1725103,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［小警告］無可否認，一守城／有佔領區就會分化","createTime":"2019-11-15T15:54:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T19:03:05.000Z","uid":94771,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"f6d201cf6ba9dbff98cac47215fb034457cb0328","tid":1725103,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T15:54:26.000Z","msg":"我唔會否認各大學的戰略價值<br />\n但對我來講，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>比起戰略價值，不分化，不割席的精神緊重要</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n路障清佐可以重組<br />\n連儂牆清佐可以重新貼返<br />\n<br />\n<strong>但精神同互相信任如果一無佐就無架啦。</strong><br />\n<br />\n次次一有佔領區，大家都好容易有分化<br />\n因為大家會有唔同意見，而且佔領區生活講不上是好，係環境唔好的時候，人係好容易做出唔理性同情緒化的行為。基於人性上<br />\n<br />\n莫講話有狗可以自出自入，輿論分化你地。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">所以如期為佐個戰略價值，而大家散收收，我寧願唔要個戰略價值。</span></strong>"},{"pid":"448864613014faa288a73636684a78d57bb35ab6","tid":1725103,"uid":310733,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T15:56:57.000Z","msg":"完全同意 一有佔領區 就係雨傘2.0"},{"pid":"f148f7192012fa4dd16cc4c826cf2e90f38d6dd2","tid":1725103,"uid":31320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T15:57:03.000Z","msg":"林鄭最驚全民天光開花，最希望示威者夜晚集中一點打陣地<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1724972\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1724972</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e5943567e35aa26b07efb04d8b53f6ddad38b0f7","tid":1725103,"uid":164752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T16:02:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"483f9a3671db1896a9adef110ee28e8630986c41","tid":1725103,"uid":55144,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T16:07:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/04/Flower_feld_18.jpg/1200px-Flower_feld_18.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fthumb%2F0%2F0